      <p>
        Passionate about building modern, scalable, and user-friendly web applications using
        <strong>Angular</strong>, <strong>PHP</strong>, and <strong>TypeScript</strong>.
        I love transforming ideas into beautiful, interactive digital experiences.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="assets/bazmi_NewResume.pdf" target="_blank" class="btn btn-gradient">ðŸ“„ Resume</a>
        <a routerLink="/projects" class="btn btn-outline">ðŸš€ View Projects</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- RIGHT: IMAGE -->
